---
title: Carb Smart Island Jerk Pork Salad with Black Beans and Mango Vinaigrette
description: Warmly-spiced jerk pork finds a cooling and sweet partner in mango chutney. Pulling double duty, this chutney serves as a glaze for the pork and also as the main flavour in the bright dressing for the black bean salad.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/salade-de-porc-aux-epices-jerk-77f46686.jpg
